<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>المَدَاخِلُ العِلْمِيَّةُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وفيه ثَلاثةُ مَدَاخِلَ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">المَدْخَلُ الأوَّلُ:</span> أَهَمِيَّةُ طَلَبِ العِلْمِ الشَّرْعِيِّ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">المَدْخَلُ الثَّانِي:</span> فَضْلُ عُلُوْمِ الغَايَةِ عَلَى عُلُوْمِ الآلَةِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">المَدْخَلُ الثَّالثُ:</span> وفيه أرْبَعُ طَلاِئِعَ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>